<template><header class="header"><a href="/" class="header__logo"><span class="header__logo-mark">M</span>Design System</a><nav class="header__nav"><a href="/" class="header__nav-link">Foundations</a><a href="/documentation/tabs.html" class="header__nav-link is-active">Components</a></nav></header><div class="layout"><nav class="layout__nav"><div class="nav"><section class="nav__section"><span class="nav__section-title">Components</span><ul class="nav__list"><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/button.html" class="nav__link">Button</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/toggle.html" class="nav__link">Toggle</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/checkbox.html" class="nav__link">Checkbox</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/input.html" class="nav__link">Input</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/select.html" class="nav__link">Select</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/radio.html" class="nav__link">Radio</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/textarea.html" class="nav__link">Textarea</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/tabs.html" class="nav__link is-active">Tabs</a></li></ul></section></div></nav><main class="layout__content"><article class="content"><span class="content__eyebrow">Components</span><h1>Tabs</h1><p class="content__lead">Navigation between related content panes with two systems: bordered <code>Tabs</code> and minimal <code>TabsSimple</code>.</p><h2 id="purpose" class="comp-section-h2">Purpose &amp; when to use</h2><ul><li>Use Tabs for sectioned content in the same context.</li><li>Use links for page navigation.</li></ul><h2 id="anatomy" class="comp-section-h2">Anatomy &amp; sizing</h2><table class="props-table"><thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Token</th><th>Value</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Tabs padding</td><td><code>--marks-spacing-20/24</code></td><td>20px 24px</td></tr><tr><td>Tabs radius</td><td><code>--marks-radius-8</code></td><td>top corners</td></tr><tr><td>TabsSimple padding</td><td><code>--marks-spacing-12/24</code></td><td>12px 24px</td></tr><tr><td>TabsSimple active border</td><td>—</td><td>2px bottom</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="variants" class="comp-section-h2">Variants &amp; all states</h2><div class="comp-demo"><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">Tabs</span><Tabs v-model="tabA" :tabs="tabsA" /></div><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">TabsSimple</span><TabsSimple v-model="tabB" :tabs="tabsB" /></div></div><h2 id="behavior" class="comp-section-h2">Behavior rules</h2><ul><li>Clicking enabled tabs emits <code>update:modelValue</code> and <code>change</code>.</li><li>Disabled tabs ignore click.</li><li>Parent controls panel rendering based on selected value.</li></ul><h2 id="content" class="comp-section-h2">Content rules</h2><ul><li>Use short, noun-like labels.</li><li>Avoid truncation and overlong tab names.</li></ul><h2 id="accessibility" class="comp-section-h2">Accessibility</h2><ul><li>Renders as buttons with keyboard focus support.</li><li>Disabled uses native attribute.</li></ul><h2 id="examples" class="comp-section-h2">Examples &amp; anti-patterns</h2><div class="comp-demo"><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">Do</span><TabsSimple v-model="tabC" :tabs="[{label:'Overview',value:'o'},{label:'Pricing',value:'p'},{label:'Availability',value:'a'}]" /></div><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label" style="color:#FD3860;">Don't</span><TabsSimple v-model="tabD" :tabs="[{label:'This is an excessively long tab title that should be avoided',value:'x'},{label:'Another very long tab',value:'y'}]" /></div></div><h2 id="api" class="comp-section-h2">API / Props</h2><table class="props-table"><thead><tr><th>Name</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>modelValue</code></td><td>String|Number</td><td>null</td><td>Selected tab value.</td></tr><tr><td><code>tabs</code></td><td>Array</td><td>required</td><td>Items with <code>{label,value,disabled?}</code>.</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="theming" class="comp-section-h2">Theming &amp; dark mode</h2><div class="comp-demo dark-preview"><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;"><TabsSimple v-model="theme" :tabs="tabsB" /></div></div></article></main><aside class="layout__aside"><div class="aside"><div class="aside__block aside__block--code"><div class="code-pane is-active"><pre><span class="token-tag">&lt;TabsSimple</span> <span class="token-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="token-string">"active"</span> <span class="token-attr">:tabs</span>=<span class="token-string">"tabs"</span> <span class="token-tag">/&gt;</span></pre></div></div></div></aside></div></template>
<script>export default{name:'TabsDocPage',data(){return{tabA:'overview',tabB:'overview',tabC:'o',tabD:'x',theme:'overview',tabsA:[{label:'Overview',value:'overview'},{label:'Pricing',value:'pricing'},{label:'Availability',value:'availability',disabled:true}],tabsB:[{label:'Overview',value:'overview'},{label:'Pricing',value:'pricing'},{label:'Availability',value:'availability'}]}}}</script>
